e it very clear that I am against violence, of any kind, <span style=\"color: red;\">by any party</span>, and at any juncture.<br />\n<br />\n算唔算"},{"pid":"06132f91f2d7b3e53aaf3dd8cf2e362f19e481fb","tid":1304023,"uid":34495,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4eee1b2d39f2b84e90adaf47ec735c067a449cf0","tid":1304023,"uid":100236,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T13:35:57.000Z","msg":"[多圖做證據]請大家不要再反本土劇愛回家了<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/dgRAkS\" target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/dgRAkS</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:07:57.000Z","msg":"你收皮啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"140dac4f8bae08e1cd8c20d4fde42e3e2a047674","tid":1304023,"uid":6132,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0c511ee9fd486991443158df3d948225e78f6482","tid":1304023,"uid":34571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:05:39.000Z","msg":"佢篇野話個人唔中意任何一方有暴力， 其實邊度有寫錯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:08:02.000Z","msg":"咁你612唔去遣責黑警暴力？<br />\n71又第一個企出嚟遣責自己啲學生？"},{"pid":"eeda39fcdeb6d87444d5fe444958e93a9103a6b0","tid":1304023,"uid":4964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:08:09.000Z","msg":"係呢個年代,做到司局長,紀律部隊首長,所有大學校長,都一定係共產黨嘅人"},{"pid":"edee9b0e1e2a81cf41311951e4429a3f981a95b4","tid":1304023,"uid":100236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06132f91f2d7b3e53aaf3dd8cf2e362f19e481fb","tid":1304023,"uid":34495,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4eee1b2d39f2b84e90adaf47ec735c067a449cf0","tid":1304023,"uid":100236,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T13:35:57.000Z","msg":"[多圖做證據]請大家不要再反本土劇愛回家了<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/dgRAkS\" target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/dgRAkS</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:07:57.000Z","msg":"你收皮啦屌你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:08:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Neo9RqP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNeo9RqP.jpg&h=cabe8b21&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5b9d567ec4f4c5a7c0e7a64343a7215aa6ab43eb","tid":1304023,"uid":75156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a544730a2366a48ca1d78ad604404ead84a5f54a","tid":1304023,"uid":21456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T13:21:30.000Z","msg":"Dear students, colleagues, alumni and friends,<br />\n<br />\nI wish to share my thoughts about the recent events. I have listened to your comments and I understand there are diverse views on my recent press statement. I also wish to take this opportunity to address concerns raised in open letters and petitions.<br />\n<br />\nLet me make it very clear that I am against violence, of any kind, by any party, and at any juncture.  As a scientist, I speak my mind. It was never my intention to please or to place blame.<br />\n<br />\nWhen I saw what was happening on the night of July 1st, I was very worried for our citizens&rsquo; lives and safety, including that of young people. Like many of you, I feared the worst. I feared we would reach the point of no return.<br />\n<br />\nAt HKU, we embrace diversity. During the past weeks, many colleagues have engaged with our students in different ways.   As always, we support our students in freely expressing themselves and we care about their safety and well-being. Academic freedom, freedom of expression, and freedom of assembly are core values of our University, and I pledge to uphold them. <br />\n<br />\nMany in Hong Kong have now spoken in the spirit of reconciliation and rebuilding trust, including the Hon Andrew Li, the First Chief Justice of the HKSAR.   But this is only the start of the healing process. We need everyone, including those in power, to seriously consider the underlying cause of the social issues and all the options and possibilities.<br />\n<br />\nWe have witnessed Hong Kong people taking to the streets peacefully. Let us continue our tradition of peaceful dissent and resolve our differences. <br />\n<br />\nI decided to come to Hong Kong after 29 years in the USA, because Hong Kong is unique, and it has tremendous potential. I am still learning about this special place, but what I have noticed most in the year I have been here is the resilience of Hong Kong, its people and its youth.<br />\n<br />\nHong Kong faces many unprecedented challenges and contentious issues. But we shall only overcome them if we begin to reach out and understand each other. Please let us work together, and with our collective wisdom, reconcile our divided society for Hong Kong&rsquo;s future.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nProfessor Xiang Zhang<br />\nPresident and Vice-Chancellor<br />\n<br />\n奶共就奶共啦 屌你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:09:23.000Z","msg":"睇到個拼音名都屌左出聲啦"},{"pid":"0d3afecda86283266172d7242d4a9f971172f927","tid":1304023,"uid":123765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eeda39fcdeb6d87444d5fe444958e93a9103a6b0","tid":1304023,"uid":4964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:08:09.000Z","msg":"係呢個年代,做到司局長,紀律部隊首長,所有大學校長,都一定係共產黨嘅人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:10:13.000Z","msg":"史維校長呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dff4a60c5eacb955ec199c2f62c6c8641e927be2","tid":1304023,"uid":1108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:12:03.000Z","msg":"唉 出左個咁嘅校長<br />\n作為舊生真係想屌佢老味自由閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c44188cea2be096ee17b38a7b70a1076f3fdfd1","tid":1304023,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89cdea8c9c5d8656fe7d52248fbaff82bdde09e3","tid":1304023,"uid":34571,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e6beb3f7732e6d13acc28079c9fc33cd2a2608a4","tid":1304023,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:06:27.000Z","msg":"against violence  <br />\n佢有冇against 警賊亂傷人，政府放縱警察濫權 ? 定係佢覺得死物比示威者更重要?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:07:34.000Z","msg":"Let me make it